.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
.idea/
.vscode/

# Cloudflare Worker source (deployed separately; carries account/db ids) - never ship or commit
**/service.subtitles.gearsai/cloudflare/
**/.wrangler/
wrangler.toml
